# -------------------------------------------------------------
# AI Agent Constraints (Genesis Template)
# -------------------------------------------------------------
# We COMMIT the following architecture to the template:
# !.specify/ (The Spec Kit Configuration)
# !.specify/memory/constitution.md (The Genesis Rules)
# !specs/ (The feature specifications)
# !.gemini/commands/, !.claude/commands/, etc. (The Agent tooling rules)

# However, we must IGNORE the agents' personal execution logs, 
# token configurations, and history so students get a clean slate.
.claude/history/
.claude/mcp.json
.gemini/logs/
.gemini/brain/*/logs/
.gemini/history/
.opencode/history/
.cursorrules

# MacOS artifacts
.DS_Store
